Build instructions
1. cd to the sorc directory
2. load modules
     # module purge
     # . ../versions/load_modules.sh ../versions/build.ver
     # WW 20210923
     # - Commented out above 2 steps
     # - Fixed version files
     # - Updated Modulefile to lua. 
     # - Version file is loaded in the build script.
     # - Run the script below to build all exec and lib
     ./build_rcdas_all.sh 
3. to build all the executables
     make clean
     make
4. to make an individual executable (not library)
     do 1, 2
     cd to appropriate directory
     make clean
     make
     cp (excutable name) ../../exec 
4. to make an individual library
   gribw:        cd gribw.cd ; make
   transutil:    cd transutil.fd; ./makelibtransutil.sh
